headline: General Mills to Webcast Fiscal 2025 Fourth Quarter and Full Year Earnings Results on June 25, 2025
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, June 04, 2025--General Mills, Inc. (NYSE: GIS) plans to report results for its fiscal 2025 fourth quarter and full year on June 25, 2025.

headline: Tariff uncertainty is hammering one of America's favorite food escapes — snacks
summary: The snacking industry has been under pressure as consumers pull back on impulse purchases amid rising prices and economic uncertainty.
